# GitHub Codespaces Integration - Company Implementation Plan

## Executive Summary

This document outlines a strategic plan to implement GitHub Codespaces integration within your CI/CD portal. This initiative will enable your development teams to launch cloud-based development environments directly from your internal portal, improving developer productivity and collaboration.

**Implementation Timeline:** 2-4 weeks  
**Required Resources:** 1-2 developers, DevOps support  
**Expected ROI:** 25-40% improvement in onboarding time, reduced local environment issues

